                                                                <div class="product__bg"></div>
                                                            </div>


                                                            <div class="product__description">
                                                                <div class="row mb-3">
                                                                    <div class="col-12">
                                                                        <h2 class="tm-page-title">What is physical abuse?</h2>
                                                                    </div>
                                                                </div>
                                                                <div class="row">
                                                                    <p>Physical abuse happens when a person uses physical force against another person. Physical abuse can start slowly and inconspicuously, for example with throwing an object or a slap, and get more intense or worse over time.</p>
                                                                    <p>
                                                                        Typical Signs are:<br>
                                                                        - shaking, slapping, pushing, punching or scratching<br>
                                                                        - kicking<br>
                                                                        - spitting or biting<br>
                                                                        - trying to strangle or choke<br>
                                                                        - using weapons<br>
                                                                        - destroying property and throwing things<br>
                                                                        - locking someone out of their house or in the house<br>
                                                                        - physical restraint e.g. pinning against the wall or bed.

                                                                    </p>

                                                                </div>

