                                                                    <p>
                                                                        Typical Signs are:<br>
                                                                        - creating fear, such as driving dangerously, possessing weapons, angry looks <br>
                                                                        - destroying  property or valued possessions<br>
                                                                        - saying that the police and the courts will not help, support or believe the victim<br>
                                                                        - threatening to ‘out’ the person<br>
