                                                                    <p>
                                                                        Typical Signs are:<br>
                                                                        - accessing personal computer files to steal images<br>
                                                                        - Photoshopping a person's image onto a sexually explicit photo or video<br>
                                                                        - staking images of a woman's cleavage or under her skirt<br>
